sequenceDiagram
  participant App
  participant Primary
  participant Wal as WAL + publication
  participant Connect as Kafka Connect
  participant Kafka
  participant Sink as JDBC sink

  App->>Primary: SQL on demo_items
  Primary->>Wal: commit + logical msg
  Connect->>Primary: poll slot (replicator user)
  Wal-->>Connect: change event
  Connect->>Kafka: produce to demopg.public.demo_items
  Kafka->>Sink: consume batch
  Sink->>Primary: INSERT/UPSERT demo_items_from_kafka
  Note over Primary,Sink: Sink table not in publication → no CDC loop
